}

p.note:
To separate the header and footer from the main content using visual effects like lines, shadows, etc, you can use a full page size artwork in SVG and set it to the default page:@page {
    background-image:url("images/my_header_footer_artwork.svg");
    background-repeat:no-repeat;
}
